    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "shared_purpose",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 1280,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 100,
      "text": "Identity resolution flow (ingress):\n  1. Contact lookup \u2192 shared.contact_info (type+value reverse-lookup)\n  2. Dedup check \u2192 shared.ingestion_events (dedupe_key unique)\n  3. Triage decision stored in ingestion_events.triage_decision\n  4. Route accepted \u2192 butler.route_inbox \u2192 target butler session\nOutbound targeting: notify(contact_id) \u2192 shared.contacts \u2192 shared.contact_info\nModel selection: shared.model_catalog + shared.butler_model_overrides",
      "originalText": "Identity resolution flow (ingress):\n  1. Contact lookup \u2192 shared.contact_info (type+value reverse-lookup)\n  2. Dedup check \u2192 shared.ingestion_events (dedupe_key unique)\n  3. Triage decision stored in ingestion_events.triage_decision\n  4. Route accepted \u2192 butler.route_inbox \u2192 target butler session\nOutbound targeting: notify(contact_id) \u2192 shared.contacts \u2192 shared.contact_info\nModel selection: shared.model_catalog + shared.butler_model_overrides",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#92400e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
