      "originalText": "shared.memory_catalog  (core_023)\n\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\nid UUID PK\nsource_schema, source_table TEXT\nsource_id UUID  (FK to canonical item)\nsource_butler TEXT\ntenant_id TEXT DEFAULT 'owner'\nentity_id UUID\nsummary TEXT\nembedding vector(384)  (IVFFlat index)\nsearch_vector tsvector  (GIN index)\nmemory_type TEXT  (fact/rule)\ncreated_at, updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ\n\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\nUNIQUE (source_schema, source_table, source_id)",
