    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "connectors_partition_note",
      "x": 1020,
      "y": 3995,
      "width": 700,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "Partition naming: filtered_events_YYYYMM\n(e.g. filtered_events_202603)\n\nPurpose:\n  Persists every message a connector\n  observes but does NOT submit to the\n  Switchboard (filtered or errored).\n  One row per filtered / errored message.\n  Full payload stored for replay.\n\nStatus lifecycle:\n  filtered \u2192 replay_pending\n         \u2192 replay_complete\n         \u2192 replay_failed\n  error   \u2192 replay_pending \u2192 ...\n\nIdentity resolution flow:\n  Connector receives message\n  \u2192 Route lookup (shared.contact_info)\n  \u2192 triage_decision in ingestion_events\n  \u2192 Switchboard route_inbox\n  \u2192 Target butler session",
      "originalText": "Partition naming: filtered_events_YYYYMM\n(e.g. filtered_events_202603)\n\nPurpose:\n  Persists every message a connector\n  observes but does NOT submit to the\n  Switchboard (filtered or errored).\n  One row per filtered / errored message.\n  Full payload stored for replay.\n\nStatus lifecycle:\n  filtered \u2192 replay_pending\n         \u2192 replay_complete\n         \u2192 replay_failed\n  error   \u2192 replay_pending \u2192 ...\n\nIdentity resolution flow:\n  Connector receives message\n  \u2192 Route lookup (shared.contact_info)\n  \u2192 triage_decision in ingestion_events\n  \u2192 Switchboard route_inbox\n  \u2192 Target butler session",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#0f766e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
